window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Chelsea</b></p> <p>You know that instinct to run when something bad is coming? Yeah. I apparently missed out on that one. Because when Damon Rose came, instead of running, I got pregnant.</p> <p><b>Damon</b></p> <p>I remember Chelsea Cross. I remember five years ago when she thought she could handle me. Proving her wrong was...enjoyable. She had hair I wanted to fist, a mouth that only stopped when I kissed it, a body that I needed to press against the nearest wall and claim.</p> <p>And now she wants a job. A smart man would say “no”. But I could teach her the same lesson I taught her five years ago.... She can’t even begin to handle me.</p>"; 
